{"tid":1036823,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"[日本沖繩冷門BAND] 7!! Seven Oops","createTime":"2019-02-25T13:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T11:04:32.000Z","uid":2646,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1bac78d79c028403187c16de176ff835eaea3ea2","tid":1036823,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.moegirl.org/common/4/4e/SevenOpps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.moegirl.org%2Fcommon%2F4%2F4e%2FSevenOpps.jpg&h=65039d39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂隊名稱由來是由於主唱NANAE名稱中前半部分是『NANA』，後半部分是『E』。NANA就是日語中7的意思，E也就是表驚嘆的「エッ!!etsu」，因此轉寫成「7!!」，念法為英語的「seven oops」。<br />\n樂隊四人為相同年級，4人在高中二年級的活動中相互認識，於2004年12月開始於沖繩地區開始活動。<br />\n<br />\n2011年，憑藉漫改電影《高校新人》的主題曲「フォーリン・ラブ」正式出道，之後承接了一些例如《火影忍者疾風傳》、《少年同盟》、《金田一少年事件簿R》等人氣動畫的片頭片尾曲，也在漫改電影《今天開始談戀愛》中獻唱。<br />\n<br />\n除上述以外，包括《四月是你的謊言》等等過去的所有動畫及漫畫的主題曲合集、7!!出道五周年紀念專輯《アニップス》已於2016年3月發行。"},{"pid":"6a2d5b264d7fc422d9c31275dee2ebbc2e1707a9","tid":1036823,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"到底有冇同好,好少人識佢地"},{"pid":"b90859fea0cfb2eac20055a12a90959f2611a7f7","tid":1036823,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"我係日本留學去過一次LIVE,好好聽"},{"pid":"a34065bf140271d7b07bcff64878ad9a4990e2b4","tid":1036823,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qG7KnMzmMU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqG7KnMzmMU4&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8YlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=2b81b047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qG7KnMzmMU4</a>"},{"pid":"c824f23b596b90f8c851d03a687e10166203fda1","tid":1036823,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Frbaf